Canonical website:
  https://github.com/credentials/silvia

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/credentials/silvia.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack silvia-0.2.2+git20160712-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./silvia-0.2.2+git20160712-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/silvia-0.2.2+git20160712-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/silvia-0.2.2+git20160712-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsilvia0-0.2.2+git20160712-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsilvia-devel-0.2.2+git20160712-X.tar.xz

